{"tid":853972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"苦戀已婚老闆　女工揮剪 工場內攀窗尋死　警破門救人","createTime":"2018-10-09T04:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T04:47:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20efa710cebbd0887959105e787a42cab098e5ca","tid":853972,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517847&d=sZljDrWenY9hBEOu%2BnkSM0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=859a8cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517847&h=bc7b124a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517847</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月09日 <br />\n<br />\n苦戀已婚老闆　女工揮剪<br />\n工場內攀窗尋死　警破門救人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09la8p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09la8p01.jpg&h=925f5574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女事主事後由救護員送院檢查。 唐家輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名持雙程證來港的內地女子，昨凌晨在火炭一間任兼職的凍肉工場，與已婚男東主為感情問題爭執，女事主執利剪揮動，東主馬上衝入房間反鎖躲避，工場內一名男工則逃離現場報警。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後反鎖工場，警方派出談判專家隔門游說，不料她突然情緒激動，打開窗戶企圖跳樓。警員立刻破門而入將女子制服並拉回安全位置，其後送院檢查，事件中幸無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n記者：唐家輝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n企圖自殘32歲女子姓石，持雙程證來港，報稱是家庭主婦。據了解，有人聲稱在火炭黃竹洋街5號富昌中心一家凍肉工場當兼職，數年前與55歲姓戴已婚的東主暗生情愫。至昨凌晨兩人因感情問題爭吵，石女情緒激動下拿起一柄利剪揮舞，嚇煞工場內眾人。<br />\n<br />\n工場內一名41歲姓陳男工見狀立刻逃出工場並報警，東主則退入另一房間反鎖躲避。警員手持盾牌到場戒備，發現石女反鎖工場，情緒依然激動，又以利剪指向喉嚨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n談判專家隔門游說<br />\n<br />\n警方其後召喚談判專家隔門游說，對方一度稍為平靜坐下。而消防員亦到場支援，在地面張開救生氣墊戒備。<br />\n<br />\n雙方對峙大約一個多小時後，女事主仍然未見平復，更忽然攀上窗花，打開窗戶企圖跳樓。警方見情況危急，別無選擇下立即以爆門工具破門入內，衝上前將女事主制服，再拉回安全位置，當時她依然不斷掙扎，稍後由救護員送院檢查。男東主見場面受控後自行開門走出房間，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n參與行動的新界南衝鋒隊第四隊，5日前亦救回一名企圖跳樓人士。上周四（4日）馬鞍山頌安邨頌群樓的36樓梯間，有一名男子危坐在石壆上企圖跳樓，事主當時背靠牆身、一隻腳伸出外牆，險象環生。<br />\n<br />\n警員得悉事主因失戀問題萌生死念後，以一句「大家都係男人，大家都明白嘅」打動事主，終花約兩小時成功勸服對方伸出雙手，將其拖回安全位置。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n劏房男疑殺人燒屋跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n捐車罅遭巴士撞　晨運翁命危"},{"pid":"883ffa2b16082a8a4f2b639baa97cc3f2731f3a9","tid":853972,"uid":43173,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/64339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F64339.jpg&h=129141b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9df60448bc0c46a22d67cd47c0d5cc0c6930c486","tid":853972,"uid":150014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"雙程證<br />\n家庭主婦<br />\n兼職<br />\n苦戀已婚老闆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc9b0f6accc7da633d039958be1da5b62e711b4","tid":853972,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9df60448bc0c46a22d67cd47c0d5cc0c6930c486","tid":853972,"uid":150014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"雙程證<br />\n家庭主婦<br />\n兼職<br />\n苦戀已婚老闆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾臭閪支雞"},{"pid":"fbc80b790173790a74599b0665e6ca2d4d49b4b2","tid":853972,"uid":70689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"公屋少婦拋棄年邁丈夫情挑肉店店東"},{"pid":"5c8a8201d49448f3e065ee215184dd130d41fca3","tid":853972,"uid":4168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fc9b0f6accc7da633d039958be1da5b62e711b4","tid":853972,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9df60448bc0c46a22d67cd47c0d5cc0c6930c486","tid":853972,"uid":150014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"雙程證<br />\n家庭主婦<br />\n兼職<br />\n苦戀已婚老闆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾臭閪支雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭雞真係害人不淺"}]}